b'tlowery1'
b'Give Online'
b'Planned Giving'
b'Give Online'
b'When you use our online giving system, you help us save time, reduce paperwork and eliminate postage. The transaction process is encrypted, so you can safely and securely support any of our campuses, colleges, units or programs.You may either make a one-time gift or set up recurring payments online using your credit card.'
b'online giving system'
b'Mail Your Check'
b'Please make gifts by check or money order payable to the \xe2\x80\x9cUniversity of Illinois Foundation\xe2\x80\x9d and include a short note (or memo on your check) stating the purpose or designation of your gift. Your gift to Rockford Medicine will be processed and receipted by our fundraising partner, the University of Illinois Foundation. For the security of your gift, please do not send cash.'
b'Mail to:'
b'University of Illinois College of Medicine Rockford Attn: Director of Development 1601 Parkview Avenue Rockford, IL 61107'
b'Gifts of Securities'
b'The College of Medicine welcomes gifts of stock, bonds, mutual funds and other appreciated securities. Gifts of appreciated securities may provide immediate assistance to us, as gifts of cash do, or may be made as part of our planned giving program to benefit the long-term needs of the College.'
b'Some benefits of gifts of appreciated securities:'
b'These gifts require special planning and consultation with your professional financial advisor, as well as University of Illinois Foundation staff. To make a gift of stock, please contact the Medical Advancement Office at the College of Medicine at (815) 395-5921 or the Foundation at (217) 333-0810.'
b'Matching Gifts'
b'Double or even triple your impact!'
b'Many employers sponsor matching gift programs and will match charitable contributions made to the University by their employees, retirees, and/or spouses.'
b'From student scholarships and technology upgrades to faculty support and innovative research, your generosity makes a powerful impact on the College\xc2\xa0\xe2\x80\x94 and on the world.'
b'To find out if your company has a matching gift policy, please\xc2\xa0search the University of Illinois Foundation\xe2\x80\x99s database. If your company is in our database, you may be able to access the forms/process needed directly through this search as well.'
b'search the University of Illinois Foundation\xe2\x80\x99s database'
b'The University of Illinois Foundation is a 501(c)3 charitable organization with EIN 37-6006007.'
b'Planned Gifts'
b'Consider a planned gift when you think about how to support the University of Illinois College of Medicine Rockford currently or how to leave a lasting legacy at the College.\xc2\xa0Learn more about planned giving options available to you.'
b'Learn more about planned giving options available to you.'
